text: Alan Brooke, 1st Viscount Alanbrooke (1883–1963) was a senior officer of the British Army. Alan Brooke may also refer to: * Alan Brooke, 3rd Viscount Brookeborough (born 1952), Northern Irish peer and landowner * Victor Brooke, 3rd Viscount Alanbrooke (Alan Victor Harold Brooke, 1932–2018), British peer * Alan Brooke (priest) (1863–1939), English academic
title: Alan Brooke (disambiguation)
